      <title>特朗普 2020 年案件在豁免裁决后被发回下级法院</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/trump-2020-case-sent-back-to-lower-court-after-immunity-ruling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院上个月裁定总统享有广泛的起诉豁免权，周五正式将针对唐纳德·特朗普干预选举的联邦刑事案件发回华盛顿的一名法官。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/trump-2020-case-sent-back-to-lower-court-after-immunity-ruling</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 17:59:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗报复性打击迫在眉睫，以色列与美国、英国合作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/israel-working-with-us-uk-as-retaliatory-strike-from-iran-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列国防官员表示，他们正在与美国和英国在伊朗预计的袭击之前进行协调，为重复今年 4 月伊朗发动的类似袭击做好准备，当时伊朗的盟友击退了袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/israel-working-with-us-uk-as-retaliatory-strike-from-iran-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 17:41:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国司法部加大力度避免选举混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/us-justice-department-steps-up-efforts-to-avoid-election-mayhem</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国司法部正在为 11 月的总统大选做准备，该部正在关注投票权斗争、调查威胁，并准备恢复与社交媒体公司的简报，以遏制错误信息的传播。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/us-justice-department-steps-up-efforts-to-avoid-election-mayhem</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 17:03:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>为什么俄罗斯人参加奥运会，而俄罗斯人却不参加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/why-russia-belarus-aren-t-competing-at-paris-olympics-but-their-athletes-are</link>
